	Playboy Foxed    
	 Los Angeles, Sept. 26 (PTI): Actress Megan Fox has caught the fancy of Playboy mogul Hugh Hefner who wants the Transformers actress to bare all for his magazine.      
	Hefner, who has made Hollywood actresses like Brigitte Bardot, Pamela Anderson, Heidi Montag, Drew Barrymore pose naked for his magazine, wants Fox to reveal all for the publication.      
	Megans a Fox!, said Hefner about the actress, who will next be seen in horror film Jennifers Body. The 24-year-old actress recently went topless for the movie.    
	Big Lohan     
	 London (PTI): Channel 4 bosses are reportedly trying to rope in Hollywoods wild child Lindsay Lohan for the last Celebrity Big Brother next year. The producers from Endemol have flown to Singapore to discuss the proposal with the star this week.    
	Star plans    
	 London (PTI): Beyonce Knowles has announced that she will wear appropriate clothing for her show in Malaysia after Islamic extremists threatened to protest at the concert. She will perform at a concert in Kuala Lumpur on October 25.                                                                                                                                                                        
